title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
itunes:title: The Best of The Dan Patrick Show
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP discusses his affliction with touching things around the studio. Legendary broadcaster  Brent Musburger shares what his relationship with Howard Cosell was. And Sunday Night Football Analyst Cris Collinsworth previews the Cowboys/Eagles matchup. Who does he like going into the game?

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
